data.description: Amazing 3 bedroom, 3.5 bath Condo in Atlanta. Features include new carpet and new interior paint throughout, spacious family room with 2 sided fireplace shared with separate dining featuring hardwood floors and access to private balcony. Great home for entertaining with family room view to kitchen with stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry and lots of cabinets. Large master suite offers private bath. 2 additional secondary bedrooms and 2 full baths on upper level. Wonderful outdoor space with gazebo. Easy Access to I-85. Not FHA Approved.
